  "texts": [
    "Data lightweighting technology can reduce the volume of collected data.",
    "Knowledge graphs are used to analyze the correlation between extracted features based on the endogenous relationship of the network protocol as well as the performance of the current network, identify the required data types, and realize data collection on demand.",
    "Real-time performance of data can be supported by setting a data update mechanism that integrates multiple update modes, such as scheduled and triggered updates, and establishing a real-time data collection protocol.",
    "A data accuracy guarantee mechanism (such as cloud-edge data collaborative calibration (Zhu et al., 2021) and resampling) must be established and appropriate data processing technologies (such as data filling, data prediction, and outlier processing) must be adopted to obtain high-precision data.",
    "Although a standardized data format is preferred, the vast number of use cases makes it impractical to define a specific data format for each scenario."
